{
    "root": {
        "data": {
            "id": "c340xosoxa00",
            "created": 1590837801249,
            "text": "Boost.Asio C++ Network Programming Cookbook",
            "hyperlink": "https://isbnsearch.org/isbn/9781783986545",
            "hyperlinkTitle": ""
        },
        "children": [
            {
                "data": {
                    "id": "c3411kmnhqo0",
                    "created": 1590838105633,
                    "text": "1 The Basics",
                    "expandState": "collapse"
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "data": {
                            "id": "c3414dyhjm80",
                            "created": 1590838326204,
                            "text": "Introduction",
                            "expandState": "collapse"
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c3430j2tnz40",
                                    "created": 1590843666113,
                                    "text": "TCP v.s. UDP",
                                    "expandState": "expand"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3414ggx9ow0",
                                            "created": 1590838331672,
                                            "text": "TCP protocol characteristics",
                                            "expandState": "collapse"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c341647v9wg0",
                                                    "created": 1590838461731,
                                                    "text": "reliable"
                                                },
                                                "children": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c34168nvft40",
                                                            "created": 1590838471406,
                                                            "text": " guarantees delivery of the messages in proper order"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c3416klw0q80",
                                                            "created": 1590838497408,
                                                            "text": "notification that the message has not been delivered"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c3416wive8w0",
                                                            "created": 1590838523347,
                                                            "text": "includes error handling mechanisms"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c3417pa8vew0",
                                                    "created": 1590838585952,
                                                    "text": "logical connection"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c34181ghqa00",
                                                    "created": 1590838612451,
                                                    "text": "point-to-point communication "
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c3418j7obsg0",
                                                    "created": 1590838651100,
                                                    "text": "stream-oriented"
                                                },
                                                "children": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c3419m8s88g0",
                                                            "created": 1590838736061,
                                                            "text": "the sent message may be broken into as many parts as the protocol wants"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c341a98dbmw0",
                                                            "created": 1590838786102,
                                                            "text": "each of them will be delivered separately, though in correct order"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c341b8dq1qg0",
                                            "created": 1590838862613,
                                            "text": "UDP protocol characteristics",
                                            "expandState": "collapse"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c341dg2oi8w0",
                                                    "created": 1590839036088,
                                                    "text": "unreliable"
                                                },
                                                "children": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c341dptwgug0",
                                                            "created": 1590839057325,
                                                            "text": "no guarantee that the message will be delivered"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c341e0taymw0",
                                                            "created": 1590839081234,
                                                            "text": "won't try to detect or fix any errors"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c341efsl2p40",
                                                    "created": 1590839113842,
                                                    "text": "connectionless"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c341epusndk0",
                                                    "created": 1590839135743,
                                                    "text": "supports both one-to-one and one-to-many communication models"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c341ex6l0b40",
                                                    "created": 1590839151694,
                                                    "text": "datagram oriented"
                                                },
                                                "children": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c341faxjp1s0",
                                                            "created": 1590839181622,
                                                            "text": "interprets data as messages of a particular size"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c341fhhr23s0",
                                                            "created": 1590839195905,
                                                            "text": "try to deliver them as a whole"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": [
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {
                                                                    "id": "c341fyvfve00",
                                                                    "created": 1590839233738,
                                                                    "text": "The message (datagram) either will be delivered as a whole"
                                                                },
                                                                "children": []
                                                            },
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {
                                                                    "id": "c341g0jfbko0",
                                                                    "created": 1590839237365,
                                                                    "text": "or if the protocol fails to do that won't be delivered at all"
                                                                },
                                                                "children": []
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c3431xtdyg80",
                                    "created": 1590843776558,
                                    "text": "API"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3431zrsn1c0",
                                            "created": 1590843780816,
                                            "text": "TCP/IP standard does not standardize the protocol API implementation"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3432o8bpqg0",
                                            "created": 1590843834058,
                                            "text": "Berkeley Sockets API is the most widely used"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c3435p0sxko0",
                                    "created": 1590844070872,
                                    "text": "Boost.Asio"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3435zmkt4o0",
                                            "created": 1590844093957,
                                            "text": "wraps raw Sockets API"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c34362q0uy00",
                                            "created": 1590844100695,
                                            "text": "provides the developer with O-O interface"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3436jvjsjk0",
                                            "created": 1590844138035,
                                            "text": "simplify network programming",
                                            "expandState": "collapse"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c3436mv0clc0",
                                                    "created": 1590844144533,
                                                    "text": "hides the raw C-style API and providing a user with an object-oriented API"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c3436vobfbc0",
                                                    "created": 1590844163719,
                                                    "text": "provides a rich-type system, which makes code more readable and allows it to catch many errors at compilation time"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c3437b96r140",
                                                    "created": 1590844197633,
                                                    "text": "cross-platform"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c3437s83w4o0",
                                                    "created": 1590844234573,
                                                    "text": "provides auxiliary functionality"
                                                },
                                                "children": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c3437tl1f5c0",
                                                            "created": 1590844237531,
                                                            "text": "scatter-gather I/O operations"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c3437y3sfzc0",
                                                            "created": 1590844247372,
                                                            "text": "stream-based I/O"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c34386fokow0",
                                                            "created": 1590844265506,
                                                            "text": "exception-based error handling"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c3438csbe3k0",
                                                            "created": 1590844279330,
                                                            "text": "others"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "data": {
                            "id": "c3438t1o7wg0",
                            "created": 1590844314724,
                            "text": "Creating an endpoint",
                            "expandState": "collapse"
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c34395vbnww0",
                                    "created": 1590844342639,
                                    "text": "endpoint",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3439nv3ra80",
                                            "created": 1590844381808,
                                            "text": "A pair of values consisting of an IP address and a protocol port number"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3439oqjs2w0",
                                            "created": 1590844383709,
                                            "text": "uniquely identifies a particular application running on a particular host in a computer network"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c343hju70b40",
                                            "created": 1590844999959,
                                            "text": "endpoints serve two goals"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c343i9osq1s0",
                                                    "created": 1590845056229,
                                                    "text": "client application"
                                                },
                                                "children": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c343ir64rg80",
                                                            "created": 1590845094282,
                                                            "text": "uses an endpoint to designate a particular server application"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c343iaq3rk80",
                                                    "created": 1590845058485,
                                                    "text": "server application"
                                                },
                                                "children": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c343jc5m86g0",
                                                            "created": 1590845139963,
                                                            "text": "uses an endpoint to specify a local IP address and a port number on which it wants to receive incoming messages"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c343jx0zpmo0",
                                                            "created": 1590845185396,
                                                            "text": "create a special endpoint representing all IP addresses at once"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c343bvorivs0",
                                    "created": 1590844555567,
                                    "text": "IP address",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c343c4bqylc0",
                                            "created": 1590844574371,
                                            "text": "IPv4"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c343cns22io0",
                                                    "created": 1590844616716,
                                                    "text": "dot-decimal notation"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c343dh8jy5c0",
                                                    "created": 1590844680840,
                                                    "text": "32-bit integer"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c343c6zdln40",
                                            "created": 1590844580153,
                                            "text": "IPv6",
                                            "expandState": "collapse"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c343cv0jf6o0",
                                                    "created": 1590844632466,
                                                    "text": "hexadecimal notation"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c343dnq3wgw0",
                                                    "created": 1590844694962,
                                                    "text": "64-bit integer"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c343evcbnsg0",
                                    "created": 1590844789907,
                                    "text": "DNS name",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c343f0jrw6g0",
                                            "created": 1590844801241,
                                            "text": "may map to multiple IP addresses"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c345wzkupwg0",
                                    "created": 1590851851905,
                                    "text": "How to do it",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c345s053q3k0",
                                            "created": 1590851461308,
                                            "text": "Creating an endpoint in the client to designate the server",
                                            "expandState": "collapse"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c345tsf6vzs0",
                                                    "created": 1590851601232,
                                                    "text": "1. Obtain the server application's IP address and port number"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c345u2375rs0",
                                                    "created": 1590851622275,
                                                    "text": "2. Represent the raw IP address as an object of the asio::ip::address class"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c345ug3aqds0",
                                                    "created": 1590851652756,
                                                    "text": "3. Instantiate the object of the asio::ip::tcp::endpoint class from the address object created in step 2 and a port number"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c345vj9hbb40",
                                                    "created": 1590851738024,
                                                    "text": "4. The endpoint is ready to be used to designate the server application"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c345w2p7mig0",
                                            "created": 1590851780334,
                                            "text": "Creating the server endpoint",
                                            "expandState": "collapse"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c345xyxgcf40",
                                                    "created": 1590851928854,
                                                    "text": "1. Obtain the protocol port number on which the server will listen for incoming requests"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c345y371nxk0",
                                                    "created": 1590851938141,
                                                    "text": "2. Create a special instance of the asio::ip::address object representing all IP addresses available on the host"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c345yy8b8s00",
                                                    "created": 1590852005698,
                                                    "text": "3. Instantiate an object of the asio::ip::tcp::endpoint class from the address object created in step 2 and a port number"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c345zufpork0",
                                                    "created": 1590852075802,
                                                    "text": "4. The endpoint is ready to be used"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c34609u6t140",
                                    "created": 1590852109329,
                                    "text": "How it works",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c346ydhveow0",
                                            "created": 1590854781673,
                                            "text": "Boost.Asio IP address type ",
                                            "expandState": "collapse"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c346ypjg6hs0",
                                                    "created": 1590854807890,
                                                    "text": "asio::ip::address_v4"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c346ywveowo0",
                                                    "created": 1590854823851,
                                                    "text": "asio::ip::address_v6"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c346z1kjop40",
                                                    "created": 1590854834078,
                                                    "text": "asio::ip::address",
                                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                                },
                                                "children": [
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c346z6q27fk0",
                                                            "created": 1590854845295,
                                                            "text": "can represent both IPv4 and IPv6 addresses"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": []
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "data": {
                                                            "id": "c3473jjgti00",
                                                            "created": 1590855186651,
                                                            "text": "not provide the any() method"
                                                        },
                                                        "children": [
                                                            {
                                                                "data": {
                                                                    "id": "c3474hjbjgg0",
                                                                    "created": 1590855260653,
                                                                    "text": "The server application must explicitly specify whether it wants to receive requests either on IPv4 or on IPv6 addresses"
                                                                },
                                                                "children": []
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c3476gr1o0g0",
                                    "created": 1590855415672,
                                    "text": "There's more",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3476vy4yag0",
                                            "created": 1590855448752,
                                            "text": "endpoint class is a specialization of the basic_endpoint<> template class"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "data": {
                            "id": "c3477h0ycsg0",
                            "created": 1590855494635,
                            "text": "Creating an active socket",
                            "expandState": "collapse"
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c3477xg5w400",
                                    "created": 1590855530383,
                                    "text": "TCP/IP standard",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c34785r6snc0",
                                            "created": 1590855548464,
                                            "text": "tells us nothing about sockets"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c3478hn0k1s0",
                                            "created": 1590855574333,
                                            "text": "tells us almost nothing about how to implement the TCP or UDP protocol software API"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c34799dn1p40",
                                            "created": 1590855634716,
                                            "text": "A developer of the protocol software is given full control over all other aspects of the API"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c347asratwg0",
                                    "created": 1590855755265,
                                    "text": "two types of sockets",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c347b3beicg0",
                                            "created": 1590855778249,
                                            "text": "active socket"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c347bv204qo0",
                                                    "created": 1590855838630,
                                                    "text": "to be used to send and receive data"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c347bwdcne00",
                                                    "created": 1590855841493,
                                                    "text": "or to initiate a connection establishment process"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c347b4mw1cw0",
                                            "created": 1590855781120,
                                            "text": "passive socket"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c347cu2rheo0",
                                                    "created": 1590855914863,
                                                    "text": "passively wait for incoming connection requests"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "data": {
                                                    "id": "c347d4lkaiw0",
                                                    "created": 1590855937768,
                                                    "text": "don't take part in user data transmission"
                                                },
                                                "children": []
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            },
                            {
                                "data": {
                                    "id": "c347deaodfc0",
                                    "created": 1590855958878,
                                    "text": "How to do it",
                                    "expandState": "collapse"
                                },
                                "children": [
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c347dpez6000",
                                            "created": 1590855983082,
                                            "text": "1. Create an instance of the asio::io_service class or use the one that has been created earlier"
                                        },
                                        "children": []
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "data": {
                                            "id": "c347eashlhk0",
                                            "created": 1590856029612,
                                            "text": "2. Create an object of the class that represents the transport layer protocol (TCP or UDP) and the version of the underlying IP protocol (IPv4 or IPv6)"
                                        },
                                        "children": [
                                            {
